<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="愛詩"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="愛詩 (feat. KAF, RIM, Harusaruhi, Isekaijoucho &amp; KOKO)"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Harusaruhi"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Isekaijoucho"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="KAF"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="KOKO"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="RIM"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="V.W.P"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="ヰ世界情緒"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="幸祜"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="春猿火"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="理芽"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="花譜"/><amll:meta key="album" value="愛詩"/><amll:meta key="album" value="愛詩 (feat. KAF, RIM, Harusaruhi, Isekaijoucho &amp; KOKO)"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPY392503155"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2695649975"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="000BaOcO2MfLCA"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="574658430"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="6n344kl5NcVT583zZhwiYi"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1807259068"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="4:21.280"><div begin="2.990" end="4:21.280"><p begin="2.990" end="11.610" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2.990" end="3.590">Cae</span><span begin="3.590" end="4.030">les</span><span begin="4.030" end="4.990">tia…</span> <span begin="5.310" end="5.610">Ae</span><span begin="5.610" end="5.980">te</span><span begin="5.980" end="6.110">r</span><span begin="6.110" end="6.450">num</span> <span begin="6.450" end="6.600">so</span><span begin="6.600" end="7.400">li</span><span begin="7.400" end="7.510">s…</span> <span begin="7.820" end="8.150">Lux</span> <span begin="8.150" end="8.630">ae</span><span begin="8.630" end="9.100">ter</span><span begin="9.100" end="11.610">na</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">苍穹… 永恒之日… 永恒之光</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">蒼穹… 永恆之日… 永恆之光</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Heavens… Eternal sun… Eternal light</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">천상이여… 영원한 태양이여… 영원한 빛이여</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Céleste... Soleil éternel... Lumière éternelle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Celestial… Sol eterno… Luz eterna</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Himmlische Sphären ewige Sonne ewiges Licht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Celestiais… Sol eterno… Luz eterna</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Небеса вечное солнце вечный свет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Celeste sole eterno luce eterna</span></p><p begin="11.980" end="17.750" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="11.980" end="12.320">き</span><span begin="12.320" end="12.650">ら</span><span begin="12.650" end="12.940">り</span><span begin="12.940" end="13.160">と</span><span begin="13.260" end="13.770">爆</span><span begin="13.770" end="14.150">ぜ</span><span begin="14.260" end="15.230">た</span><span begin="15.470" end="15.840">輪廻</span><span begin="15.840" end="16.270">の</span><span begin="16.270" end="17.750">中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">璀璨光芒炸裂于轮回之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">璀璨光芒炸裂於輪迴之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Inside the reincarnation that burst with a sparkle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">반짝이며 터진 윤회 속</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans le cycle de réincarnation qui a éclaté avec éclat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En medio de la reencarnación que estalló con un destello</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Im strahlend zerplatzenden Kreislauf der Wiedergeburt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No meio da reencarnação que explodiu com um brilho</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В сияющей вспышке круговорота перерождений</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nel ciclo della reincarnazione esploso con un bagliore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kirari to hazeta toki no naka</span></p><p begin="18.000" end="23.480" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="18.000" end="18.880">空</span><span begin="18.880" end="19.330">を</span><span begin="19.330" end="19.950">見</span><span begin="19.950" end="20.620">る</span> <span begin="20.880" end="20.900">「</span><span begin="20.900" end="21.060">そ</span><span begin="21.060" end="21.230">し</span><span begin="21.230" end="21.380">て</span><span begin="21.380" end="21.540">ボ</span><span begin="21.540" end="21.740">ク</span><span begin="21.740" end="22.020">は</span><span begin="22.020" end="22.670">選</span><span begin="22.670" end="23.450">ぶ</span><span begin="23.450" end="23.480">」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仰望天空 「而后我做出了抉择」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">仰望天空 「而後我做出了抉擇」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Looking at the sky &quot;And I choose&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하늘을 봐 「그리고 나는 선택해」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je regarde le ciel « Et je choisis »</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Miro al cielo «y entonces yo elijo»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich schaue in den Himmel und ich wähle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Olhando para o céu «E então eu escolho»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я смотрю в небо «И я делаю выбор»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Guardo il cielo «E io scelgo»</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sora o miru &quot;Soshite boku wa erabu&quot;</span></p><p begin="23.760" end="27.590" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="23.760" end="24.090">難</span><span begin="24.090" end="24.280">易</span><span begin="24.280" end="24.580">度</span><span begin="24.580" end="24.880">エー</span><span begin="24.880" end="25.050">ス</span><span begin="25.050" end="25.380">級</span><span begin="25.380" end="25.690">の</span><span begin="25.690" end="26.020">支</span><span begin="26.020" end="26.360">配</span><span begin="26.360" end="26.480">ディ</span><span begin="26.480" end="26.650">ス</span><span begin="26.650" end="26.820">ト</span><span begin="26.820" end="27.130">ピ</span><span begin="27.130" end="27.590">ア</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">直面难度S级的支配型反乌托邦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">直面難度S級的支配型反烏托邦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A ruling dystopia of ace-level difficulty</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">난이도 에이스급의 지배 디스토피아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une dystopie dominante d&apos;une difficulté de niveau as</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una distopía de control con dificultad de clase as</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eine beherrschende Dystopie von höchstem Schwierigkeitsgrad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Uma distopia de dominação com nível de dificuldade ás</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Управляемая антиутопия высочайшего уровня сложности</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Una distopia di dominio con difficoltà di livello asso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nan&apos;ido eesu kyuu no shihai disutopia</span></p><p begin="27.910" end="33.580" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="27.910" end="28.250">そ</span><span begin="28.250" end="28.410">ん</span><span begin="28.410" end="28.560">な</span><span begin="28.560" end="28.900">社</span><span begin="28.900" end="29.540">会</span><span begin="29.540" end="29.690">に</span><span begin="29.690" end="29.980">鉄</span><span begin="29.980" end="30.480">槌</span><span begin="30.480" end="30.800">の</span><span begin="30.800" end="31.100">ボ</span><span begin="31.100" end="31.960">タ</span><span begin="31.960" end="32.080">ン</span><span begin="32.080" end="32.240">だ</span><span begin="32.240" end="33.580">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若那是对这社会降下铁锤的按钮</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若那是對這社會降下鐵錘的按鈕</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Calling it a button for the iron hammer to such a society</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그런 사회에 철퇴를 내릴 버튼이라며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Disant que c&apos;est le bouton d&apos;un marteau de fer pour une telle société</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Diciendo que es el botón del martillo de hierro para esta sociedad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass dies der Knopf für den Hammer in solch einer Gesellschaft sei</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dizendo que é o botão do martelo de ferro para tal sociedade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Говоря что это кнопка карающего молота для такого общества</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dicono che sia il pulsante per calare il martello su una società del genere</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sonna shakai ni tettsui no botan da to</span></p><p begin="33.660" end="36.140" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="33.660" end="34.000">狂</span><span begin="34.000" end="34.160">っ</span><span begin="34.160" end="34.300">た</span><span begin="34.300" end="34.690">正</span><span begin="34.790" end="35.080">義</span><span begin="35.080" end="35.210">は</span><span begin="35.210" end="35.590">静</span><span begin="35.590" end="35.930">か</span><span begin="35.930" end="36.140">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">疯狂的正义悄无声息地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">瘋狂的正義悄無聲息地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Mad justice quietly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">미쳐버린 정의는 고요하게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La justice folle silencieusement</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La justicia enloquecida en silencio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die verrückt gewordene Gerechtigkeit hat leise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A justiça enlouquecida silenciosamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Безумная справедливость тихо</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La giustizia impazzita silenziosamente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kurutta seigi wa shizuka ni</span></p><p begin="36.180" end="43.560" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.180" end="36.380">ヒ</span><span begin="36.380" end="36.540">ト</span><span begin="36.540" end="36.680">の</span><span begin="36.680" end="36.870">す</span><span begin="36.870" end="37.040">べ</span><span begin="37.040" end="37.230">て</span><span begin="37.330" end="37.640">燃</span><span begin="37.640" end="37.800">や</span><span begin="37.800" end="38.030">し</span><span begin="38.130" end="38.470">た</span><span begin="38.470" end="38.850">の</span> <span begin="39.100" end="39.560">Ha</span><span begin="39.560" end="40.030">ha</span><span begin="40.030" end="40.530">ha</span><span begin="40.530" end="40.890">と</span><span begin="41.010" end="42.250">笑</span><span begin="42.250" end="42.470">っ</span><span begin="42.470" end="43.560">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">将人类的一切焚烧殆尽 哈哈哈地嗤笑着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">將人類的一切焚燒殆盡 哈哈哈地嗤笑著</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Burned everything human away laughing Hahaha</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">인간의 모든 것을 불태웠어 하하하 하고 웃으며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">A brûlé tout ce qui est humain en riant Hahaha</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quemó todo de la humanidad riéndose Jajaja</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Alles Menschliche verbrannt lachend mit einem Hahaha</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Queimou tudo dos humanos rindo Hahaha</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сожгла всё человеческое со смехом Ха-ха-ха</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ha bruciato tutto dell&apos;umanità ridendo ah ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hito no subete moyashita no Hahaha to waratte</span></p><p begin="43.840" end="46.010" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="43.840" end="44.200">そ</span><span begin="44.200" end="44.350">れ</span><span begin="44.350" end="44.520">で</span><span begin="44.520" end="44.780">も</span><span begin="44.780" end="45.010">咲</span><span begin="45.010" end="45.460">い</span><span begin="45.460" end="45.670">た</span><span begin="45.670" end="46.010">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">即便如此依然绽放</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">即便如此依然綻放</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even so it bloomed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그럼에도 피어났어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Malgré tout elle a fleuri tu sais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aun así floreció</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Trotzdem hat sie geblüht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo assim desabrochou</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но он всё равно расцвёл</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Eppure è sbocciato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Soredemo saita yo</span></p><p begin="46.410" end="48.620" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="46.410" end="46.750">焼</span><span begin="46.750" end="46.910">け</span><span begin="46.910" end="47.060">野</span><span begin="47.060" end="47.560">原</span><span begin="47.560" end="47.990">の</span><span begin="47.990" end="48.620">下</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就在这片焦土之下</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就在這片焦土之下</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Under the burned field</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">불타버린 들판 아래</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sous la plaine ravagée par les flammes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Debajo del campo quemado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Unter der verbrannten Erde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sob o campo queimado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">На выжженной земле</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sotto il campo bruciato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yakenohara no shita</span></p><p begin="48.960" end="52.800" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.960" end="49.910">小</span><span begin="49.910" end="50.300">さ</span><span begin="50.300" end="50.740">な</span><span begin="50.920" end="51.420">花</span><span begin="51.420" end="52.800">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那小小的花儿</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那小小的花兒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A small flower</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">작은 꽃은</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La petite fleur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una pequeña flor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die kleine Blume</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A pequena flor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Маленький цветок</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il piccolo fiore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Chiisana hana wa</span></p><p begin="53.130" end="55.260" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="53.130" end="53.470">Sin</span><span begin="53.470" end="53.920">ging</span> <span begin="53.920" end="54.090">a</span> <span begin="54.090" end="55.260">song</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">高唱着歌谣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">高唱著歌謠</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">노래를 불러</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Chantant une chanson</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cantando una canción</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Lied singend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Cantando uma canção</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пою песню</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Cantando una canzone</span></p><p begin="55.710" end="1:02.120" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="55.710" end="56.010">ボ</span><span begin="56.010" end="56.310">ク</span><span begin="56.310" end="56.640">は</span><span begin="56.640" end="56.950">ボ</span><span begin="56.950" end="57.130">ク</span><span begin="57.130" end="57.290">の</span><span begin="57.290" end="57.760">物</span><span begin="57.760" end="58.400">語</span><span begin="58.400" end="58.790">を</span><span begin="59.030" end="59.360">運</span><span begin="59.360" end="59.670">命</span><span begin="59.670" end="59.800">の</span><span begin="59.800" end="1:00.050">せ</span><span begin="1:00.050" end="1:00.210">い</span><span begin="1:00.350" end="1:00.640">に</span><span begin="1:00.640" end="1:00.780">は</span><span begin="1:00.780" end="1:01.120">し</span><span begin="1:01.120" end="1:01.440">た</span><span begin="1:01.440" end="1:01.770">く</span><span begin="1:01.770" end="1:02.030">な</span><span begin="1:02.030" end="1:02.120">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我不愿将属于我的故事归咎于命运</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我不願將屬於我的故事歸咎於命運</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I don&apos;t want to blame my story on destiny</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나는 나의 이야기를 운명 탓으로 돌리고 싶지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne veux pas rejeter la faute de mon histoire sur le destin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No quiero culpar al destino por mi propia historia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich möchte meine Geschichte nicht dem Schicksal anlasten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu não quero culpar o destino pela minha história</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я не хочу винить судьбу в своей истории</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non voglio dare la colpa al destino per la mia storia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku wa boku no monogatari o unmei no sei ni wa shitakunai</span></p><p begin="1:02.390" end="1:06.560" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:02.390" end="1:02.880">一</span><span begin="1:02.880" end="1:03.300">歩</span><span begin="1:03.650" end="1:04.160">一</span><span begin="1:04.160" end="1:04.460">歩</span><span begin="1:04.460" end="1:04.630">づ</span><span begin="1:04.630" end="1:04.800">つ</span><span begin="1:04.800" end="1:05.080">を</span><span begin="1:05.080" end="1:05.240">い</span><span begin="1:05.240" end="1:05.440">き</span><span begin="1:05.440" end="1:06.060">てい</span><span begin="1:06.060" end="1:06.560">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一步一步切实地活下去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">一步一步切實地活下去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Living step by step</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">한 걸음 한 걸음씩 살아갈 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je vis en avançant pas à pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Voy viviendo paso a paso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gehe Schritt für Schritt durchs Leben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vou vivendo um passo de cada vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я буду жить шаг за шагом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Continuo a vivere passo dopo passo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ippo ippo zutsu o ikiteiku</span></p><p begin="1:06.850" end="1:09.000" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:06.850" end="1:07.360">雑</span><span begin="1:07.360" end="1:07.820">音</span><span begin="1:07.820" end="1:08.000">地</span><span begin="1:08.000" end="1:08.470">獄</span><span begin="1:08.470" end="1:08.650">だ</span><span begin="1:08.650" end="1:08.810">ろ</span><span begin="1:08.810" end="1:08.970">う</span><span begin="1:08.970" end="1:09.000">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这里是充满杂音的地狱吧？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這裡是充滿雜音的地獄吧？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s a noise hell isn&apos;t it?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">잡음 지옥이겠지?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est un enfer de bruits parasites n&apos;est-ce pas ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Es un infierno de ruido verdad?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es ist eine Lärmhölle oder?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">É um inferno de ruídos não é?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это ведь шумовой ад не так ли?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sarà un inferno di rumori vero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zatsuon jigoku darou?</span></p><p begin="1:09.250" end="1:12.120" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:09.250" end="1:09.420">そ</span><span begin="1:09.420" end="1:09.590">れ</span><span begin="1:09.590" end="1:09.720">で</span><span begin="1:09.720" end="1:09.880">も</span><span begin="1:09.880" end="1:10.050">こ</span><span begin="1:10.050" end="1:10.210">の</span><span begin="1:10.210" end="1:10.850">偽</span><span begin="1:10.850" end="1:10.990">の</span><span begin="1:10.990" end="1:11.310">世</span><span begin="1:11.310" end="1:11.970">界</span><span begin="1:11.970" end="1:12.120">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">即便如此 在这虚伪的世界中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">即便如此 在這虛偽的世界中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even so in this fake world</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래도 이 거짓된 세계에</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Malgré tout dans ce monde factice</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aun así en este mundo falso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dennoch in dieser falschen Welt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo assim neste mundo falso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И всё же в этом фальшивом мире</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Eppure in questo mondo falso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Soredemo kono nise no sekai ni</span></p><p begin="1:12.280" end="1:14.680" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.280" end="1:12.440">た</span><span begin="1:12.440" end="1:12.510">っ</span><span begin="1:12.510" end="1:12.630">た</span><span begin="1:12.630" end="1:12.910">の</span><span begin="1:12.910" end="1:13.000">ひ</span><span begin="1:13.000" end="1:13.110">と</span><span begin="1:13.110" end="1:13.240">つ</span><span begin="1:13.240" end="1:13.550">だ</span><span begin="1:13.550" end="1:13.700">け</span><span begin="1:13.700" end="1:13.920">で</span><span begin="1:13.920" end="1:14.050">い</span><span begin="1:14.050" end="1:14.190">い</span><span begin="1:14.190" end="1:14.390">ん</span><span begin="1:14.390" end="1:14.680">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仅此唯一的那个就已足够</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">僅此唯一的那個就已足夠</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Just one is fine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">단 하나라도 좋아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un seul me suffit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Basta con que haya solo uno</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Reicht ein einziges aus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Basta apenas uma única coisa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мне достаточно всего одной</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ne basta soltanto una</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tatta no hitotsu dake de iinda</span></p><p begin="1:14.830" end="1:16.990" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:14.830" end="1:14.990">ジ</span><span begin="1:14.990" end="1:15.110">ブ</span><span begin="1:15.110" end="1:15.190">ン</span><span begin="1:15.190" end="1:15.480">の</span><span begin="1:15.480" end="1:15.720">色</span><span begin="1:15.720" end="1:15.810">し</span><span begin="1:15.810" end="1:16.150">た</span><span begin="1:16.150" end="1:16.790">歌</span><span begin="1:16.790" end="1:16.990">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">将那有着自我色彩的歌谣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">將那有著自我色彩的歌謠</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A song in my own color</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 고유의 색을 띤 노래를</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une chanson teintée de ma propre couleur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una canción con mi propio color</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Lied in meiner eigenen Farbe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Uma canção com a minha própria cor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Песни окрашенной в мой цвет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Una canzone dipinta del mio colore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jibun no iro shita uta o</span></p><p begin="1:17.040" end="1:21.340" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:17.040" end="1:17.400">こ</span><span begin="1:17.400" end="1:17.530">の</span><span begin="1:17.530" end="1:18.220">星</span><span begin="1:18.220" end="1:18.670">の</span><span begin="1:18.670" end="1:19.630">歴史</span><span begin="1:19.630" end="1:20.550">に</span><span begin="1:20.550" end="1:20.750">添</span><span begin="1:20.750" end="1:20.920">え</span><span begin="1:20.920" end="1:21.340">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">添入这颗星球的历史</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">添入這顆星球的歷史</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Adding it to the history of this planet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 별의 역사에 곁들여</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">L&apos;ajoutant à l&apos;histoire de cette planète</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Para añadirla a la historia de este planeta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der Geschichte dieses Planeten beizufügen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Acrescentando-a à história deste planeta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чтобы вплести её в историю этой планеты</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Da aggiungere alla storia di questo pianeta</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono hoshi no kioku ni soete</span></p><p begin="1:21.570" end="1:24.820" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:21.570" end="1:21.910">風</span><span begin="1:21.910" end="1:22.040">に</span><span begin="1:22.040" end="1:22.560">還</span><span begin="1:22.560" end="1:24.820">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">随后回归风中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">隨後回歸風中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Returning to the wind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">바람으로 돌아가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je retourne au vent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y regresar al viento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bevor ich zum Wind zurückkehre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Retorno ao vento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И вернуться к ветру</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E tornare al vento</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kaze ni kaeru</span></p><p begin="1:27.250" end="1:35.220" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:27.250" end="1:27.830">ひ</span><span begin="1:27.830" end="1:28.260">ら</span><span begin="1:28.260" end="1:29.170">り</span><span begin="1:29.470" end="1:29.870">は</span><span begin="1:29.870" end="1:30.330">ら</span><span begin="1:30.330" end="1:30.680">り</span><span begin="1:30.780" end="1:31.670">と</span><span begin="1:32.090" end="1:32.420">舞</span><span begin="1:32.420" end="1:32.850">い</span><span begin="1:32.850" end="1:33.340">飛</span><span begin="1:33.340" end="1:35.220">ぶ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">飘飘荡荡 漫天飞舞</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">飄飄蕩蕩 漫天飛舞</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Fluttering and dancing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하늘하늘 춤추며 날아다니는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Voltigeant et voletant dans les airs</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Revoloteando y danzando en el aire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Leicht und sanft umherflatternd</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Voando e dançando levemente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Легко и плавно кружась в танце</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Danzando e volando via leggeri</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hirari harari to maitobu</span></p><p begin="1:36.210" end="1:44.800" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:36.210" end="1:36.890">一</span><span begin="1:36.890" end="1:37.510">面</span><span begin="1:37.510" end="1:37.930">の</span><span begin="1:37.930" end="1:38.370">果</span><span begin="1:38.470" end="1:39.390">て</span> <span begin="1:39.710" end="1:40.050">花</span><span begin="1:40.050" end="1:40.410">び</span><span begin="1:40.510" end="1:41.000">ら</span><span begin="1:41.000" end="1:42.150">で</span><span begin="1:42.270" end="1:42.640">埋</span><span begin="1:42.640" end="1:43.080">め</span><span begin="1:43.080" end="1:43.570">尽</span><span begin="1:43.570" end="1:44.090">く</span><span begin="1:44.210" end="1:44.800">す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">直至视野尽头 皆被花瓣填满</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">直至視野盡頭 皆被花瓣填滿</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Filling the end of the whole surface with petals</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">끝없는 들판을 꽃잎으로 가득 채워</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Recouvrant tout jusqu&apos;au bout de l&apos;horizon de pétales</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Llenando por completo de pétalos los confines del lugar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Ende des Horizonts ganz mit Blütenblättern bedeckend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Preenchendo os confins de toda a superfície com pétalas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">До самого горизонта всё заполнено лепестками</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ricoprendo di petali i confini dell&apos;orizzonte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ichimen no hate hanabira de umetsukusu</span></p><p begin="1:45.080" end="1:47.710" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:45.080" end="1:45.110">「</span><span begin="1:45.110" end="1:45.330">そ</span><span begin="1:45.330" end="1:45.480">ん</span><span begin="1:45.480" end="1:45.590">な</span><span begin="1:45.590" end="1:45.800">日</span><span begin="1:45.800" end="1:45.960">を</span><span begin="1:45.960" end="1:46.770">夢</span><span begin="1:46.770" end="1:46.910">見</span><span begin="1:46.910" end="1:47.680">て</span><span begin="1:47.680" end="1:47.710">」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">「梦见那样的日子」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">「夢見那樣的日子」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">&quot;Dreaming of such a day&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">「그런 날을 꿈꾸며」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">« En rêvant d&apos;un tel jour »</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">«Soñando con un día así»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Von solch einem Tag träumend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">«Sonhando com um dia assim»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">«Мечтая о таком дне»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">«Sognando un giorno del genere»</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">&quot;Sonna hi o yumemite&quot;</span></p><p begin="1:48.020" end="1:51.970" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:48.020" end="1:48.340">意</span><span begin="1:48.340" end="1:48.500">味</span><span begin="1:48.500" end="1:48.820">不</span><span begin="1:48.820" end="1:49.160">レ</span><span begin="1:49.160" end="1:49.310">ベ</span><span begin="1:49.310" end="1:49.640">ル</span><span begin="1:49.640" end="1:49.930">の</span><span begin="1:49.930" end="1:50.280">可</span><span begin="1:50.280" end="1:50.570">能</span><span begin="1:50.570" end="1:50.930">性</span><span begin="1:50.930" end="1:51.080">を</span><span begin="1:51.080" end="1:51.430">追</span><span begin="1:51.430" end="1:51.970">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">追寻着近乎毫无意义的可能性</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">追尋著近乎毫無意義的可能性</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Chasing possibilities of an incomprehensible level</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">의미불명 수준의 가능성을 쫓아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Poursuivant des possibilités à un niveau incompréhensible</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Persigo posibilidades de un nivel incomprensible</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Unbegreiflichen Möglichkeiten nachjagend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Perseguindo uma possibilidade de nível incompreensível</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В погоне за шансами непостижимого уровня</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Inseguendo possibilità di livello incomprensibile</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Imifu reberu no kanousei o ou</span></p><p begin="1:52.150" end="1:57.640" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:52.150" end="1:52.510">人</span><span begin="1:52.630" end="1:53.040">生</span><span begin="1:53.140" end="1:53.360">は</span><span begin="1:53.480" end="1:53.760">無</span><span begin="1:53.760" end="1:53.950">理</span><span begin="1:53.950" end="1:54.450">ゲー</span><span begin="1:54.450" end="1:54.760">の</span><span begin="1:54.760" end="1:55.360">連</span><span begin="1:55.360" end="1:56.490">続</span><span begin="1:56.490" end="1:57.640">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">人生就是接连不断的超高难游戏</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">人生就是接連不斷的超高難遊戲</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Life is a series of impossible games</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">인생은 억지 게임의 연속이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La vie est une succession de jeux impossibles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La vida es una serie de juegos imposibles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Leben ist eine Abfolge von unmöglichen Spielen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A vida é uma sucessão de jogos impossíveis</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Жизнь это череда непроходимых игр</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La vita è un susseguirsi di giochi impossibili</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jinsei wa murigee no renzoku da</span></p><p begin="1:57.920" end="2:00.400" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:57.920" end="1:58.120">ど</span><span begin="1:58.120" end="1:58.240">の</span><span begin="1:58.240" end="1:58.410">宇</span><span begin="1:58.410" end="1:58.740">宙</span><span begin="1:58.740" end="1:59.020">の</span><span begin="1:59.020" end="1:59.360">と</span><span begin="1:59.360" end="1:59.520">き</span><span begin="1:59.520" end="1:59.730">だ</span><span begin="1:59.730" end="1:59.840">っ</span><span begin="1:59.840" end="2:00.090">た</span><span begin="2:00.090" end="2:00.160">っ</span><span begin="2:00.160" end="2:00.400">け</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">究竟是在哪个宇宙的时候呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">究竟是在哪個宇宙的時候呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Which universe&apos;s time was it again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어느 우주 때였더라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;était dans quel univers déjà</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En qué universo fue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In welchem Universum war das noch gleich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Em qual universo foi mesmo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В какой же это было вселенной</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In quale universo era</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dono uchuu no toki datta kke</span></p><p begin="2:00.470" end="2:07.980" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.470" end="2:00.770">電</span><span begin="2:00.770" end="2:00.990">車</span><span begin="2:00.990" end="2:01.150">の</span><span begin="2:01.150" end="2:01.460">窓</span><span begin="2:01.600" end="2:01.950">に</span><span begin="2:01.950" end="2:02.590">映</span><span begin="2:02.590" end="2:02.700">っ</span><span begin="2:02.700" end="2:03.140">た</span><span begin="2:03.340" end="2:03.720">ジ</span><span begin="2:03.830" end="2:04.280">ブ</span><span begin="2:04.280" end="2:04.660">ン</span><span begin="2:04.760" end="2:05.300">は</span><span begin="2:05.300" end="2:05.580">見</span><span begin="2:05.580" end="2:06.510">た</span><span begin="2:06.510" end="2:06.690">く</span><span begin="2:06.690" end="2:07.870">な</span><span begin="2:07.870" end="2:07.980">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">实在不愿看见映在电车窗上的自己</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">實在不願看見映在電車窗上的自己</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I didn&apos;t want to see myself reflected in the train window</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">전철 창문에 비친 내 모습은 보기 싫어서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne voulais pas voir mon reflet dans la vitre du train</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No quería ver mi propio reflejo en la ventana del tren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich wollte mein eigenes Spiegelbild im Zugfenster nicht sehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu não queria ver o meu reflexo na janela do trem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я не хотела смотреть на своё отражение в окне поезда</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non volevo vedere me stessa riflessa nel finestrino del treno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Densha no mado ni utsutta jibun wa mitakunaku</span></p><p begin="2:08.130" end="2:10.290" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:08.130" end="2:08.460">で</span><span begin="2:08.460" end="2:08.620">も</span><span begin="2:08.620" end="2:08.790">ど</span><span begin="2:08.790" end="2:09.090">の</span><span begin="2:09.090" end="2:09.270">世</span><span begin="2:09.270" end="2:09.750">界</span><span begin="2:09.750" end="2:09.930">で</span><span begin="2:09.930" end="2:10.290">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">可是无论在哪个世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">可是無論在哪個世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">But in any world</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하지만 어떤 세계에서든</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mais dans n&apos;importe quel monde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pero en cualquier mundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Aber in jeder Welt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mas em qualquer mundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но в каком бы то ни было мире</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ma in qualunque mondo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Demo dono sekai demo</span></p><p begin="2:10.690" end="2:16.960" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:10.690" end="2:11.020">ヒ</span><span begin="2:11.020" end="2:11.200">ト</span><span begin="2:11.200" end="2:11.350">は</span><span begin="2:11.350" end="2:11.680">発</span><span begin="2:11.680" end="2:11.840">つ</span><span begin="2:11.840" end="2:12.300">こ</span><span begin="2:12.300" end="2:12.510">と</span><span begin="2:12.510" end="2:12.900">を</span><span begin="2:13.230" end="2:13.750">や</span><span begin="2:13.750" end="2:14.210">め</span><span begin="2:14.210" end="2:14.540">な</span><span begin="2:14.540" end="2:14.930">か</span><span begin="2:14.930" end="2:15.190">っ</span><span begin="2:15.190" end="2:15.520">た</span><span begin="2:15.520" end="2:15.690">ん</span><span begin="2:15.690" end="2:16.960">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">人类都不曾停下出发的脚步</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">人類都不曾停下出發的腳步</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Humans never stopped departing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">인간은 떠나는 것을 멈추지 않았어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les humains n&apos;ont jamais cessé de partir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La humanidad nunca dejó de partir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Haben die Menschen nie aufgehört aufzubrechen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As pessoas não pararam de partir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Люди не переставали отправляться в путь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">L&apos;umanità non ha mai smesso di partire</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hito wa tatsu koto o yamenakattanda</span></p><p begin="2:17.360" end="2:19.470" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:17.360" end="2:17.720">Sin</span><span begin="2:17.720" end="2:18.170">ging</span> <span begin="2:18.170" end="2:18.370">a</span> <span begin="2:18.370" end="2:19.470">life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">讴歌生命</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">謳歌生命</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">삶을 노래해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Chantant une vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cantando una vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Leben singend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Cantando uma vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пою жизнь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Cantando una vita</span></p><p begin="2:19.910" end="2:22.970" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:19.910" end="2:20.260">き</span><span begin="2:20.260" end="2:20.590">っ</span><span begin="2:20.590" end="2:20.890">と</span><span begin="2:20.890" end="2:21.230">過</span><span begin="2:21.230" end="2:21.380">去</span> <span begin="2:21.380" end="2:21.860">現</span><span begin="2:21.860" end="2:22.340">在</span> <span begin="2:22.340" end="2:22.510">未</span><span begin="2:22.510" end="2:22.970">来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论是过去 现在 还是未来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論是過去 現在 還是未來</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Surely past present future</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">분명 과거 현재 미래</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sûrement le passé le présent l&apos;avenir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Seguramente el pasado presente futuro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sicherlich Vergangenheit Gegenwart Zukunft</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Com certeza passado presente futuro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Наверняка прошлое настоящее и будущее</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sicuramente passato presente e futuro</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kitto kako genzai mirai</span></p><p begin="2:23.280" end="2:26.240" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:23.280" end="2:23.450">ぐ</span><span begin="2:23.450" end="2:23.610">る</span><span begin="2:23.610" end="2:23.790">ぐ</span><span begin="2:23.790" end="2:23.930">る</span><span begin="2:23.930" end="2:24.280">回</span><span begin="2:24.280" end="2:24.430">る</span><span begin="2:24.550" end="2:25.060">神</span><span begin="2:25.060" end="2:25.360">の</span><span begin="2:25.360" end="2:25.570">手</span><span begin="2:25.570" end="2:25.700">の</span><span begin="2:25.700" end="2:26.240">上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">都定在神明的手掌之上不停轮回</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">都定在神明的手掌之上不停輪迴</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">On the hand of God spinning round and round</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">빙글빙글 도는 신의 손 위</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tournant en rond sur la main de Dieu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Girando y dando vueltas sobre la palma de Dios</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Drehen sich im Kreis auf der Handfläche Gottes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Girando e girando na palma da mão de Deus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Беспрестанно вращаются на ладони бога</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sulla mano di Dio che gira in tondo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Guruguru mawaru kami no te no ue</span></p><p begin="2:26.620" end="2:30.760" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:26.620" end="2:27.140">僕</span><span begin="2:27.140" end="2:27.540">は</span><span begin="2:27.920" end="2:28.440">迷</span><span begin="2:28.440" end="2:28.730">い</span><span begin="2:28.730" end="2:28.880">な</span><span begin="2:28.880" end="2:29.080">が</span><span begin="2:29.080" end="2:29.370">ら</span><span begin="2:29.370" end="2:29.510">も</span><span begin="2:29.510" end="2:29.700">い</span><span begin="2:29.700" end="2:30.320">き</span><span begin="2:30.320" end="2:30.760">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我哪怕迷茫也依然活了过来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我哪怕迷茫也依然活了過來</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I lived while hesitating</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나는 헤매면서도 살아왔어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J&apos;ai vécu tout en étant perdue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Yo viví aunque estuviera perdida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich habe gelebt auch wenn ich mich verirrte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu vivi mesmo estando perdida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я жила хоть и блуждала в сомнениях</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Io ho vissuto anche se mi sono smarrita</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku wa mayoinagara mo ikita</span></p><p begin="2:31.100" end="2:33.190" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:31.100" end="2:31.430">う</span><span begin="2:31.430" end="2:31.590">ま</span><span begin="2:31.590" end="2:31.760">く</span><span begin="2:31.760" end="2:32.080">言</span><span begin="2:32.080" end="2:32.250">え</span><span begin="2:32.250" end="2:32.550">な</span><span begin="2:32.550" end="2:32.710">い</span><span begin="2:32.710" end="2:32.880">け</span><span begin="2:32.880" end="2:33.190">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">虽说没法很好地言说</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">雖說沒法很好地言說</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can&apos;t say it well but</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">말로 잘 표현할 순 없지만</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je n&apos;arrive pas bien à le dire mais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No puedo decirlo bien pero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich kann es nicht gut in Worte fassen aber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não consigo dizer direito mas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Не могу подобрать слова но</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non riesco a dirlo bene ma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Umaku ienai kedo</span></p><p begin="2:33.490" end="2:36.490" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:33.490" end="2:33.710">そ</span><span begin="2:33.710" end="2:33.840">ん</span><span begin="2:33.840" end="2:34.000">な</span><span begin="2:34.000" end="2:34.290">迷</span><span begin="2:34.290" end="2:34.470">い</span><span begin="2:34.470" end="2:34.750">が</span><span begin="2:34.750" end="2:34.780">「</span><span begin="2:34.780" end="2:35.110">生</span><span begin="2:35.110" end="2:35.300">き</span><span begin="2:35.300" end="2:35.480">る</span><span begin="2:35.480" end="2:35.510">」</span><span begin="2:35.510" end="2:35.590">っ</span><span begin="2:35.590" end="2:35.900">て</span><span begin="2:35.900" end="2:36.220">こ</span><span begin="2:36.220" end="2:36.490">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">但那份迷茫正是「活着」这回事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">但那份迷茫正是「活著」這回事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Such hesitation is what it means to &quot;live&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그런 헤맴이 「살아간다」는 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ces hésitations sont ce que signifie « vivre »</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esa vacilación es lo que significa «vivir»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Solch ein Verirren bedeutet zu leben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Essa hesitação é o que significa «viver»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Эти сомнения это и значит «жить»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quell&apos;esitazione è ciò che significa «vivere»</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sonna mayoi ga &quot;ikiru&quot; tte koto</span></p><p begin="2:36.510" end="2:38.890" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:36.510" end="2:36.760">伝</span><span begin="2:36.760" end="2:36.880">え</span><span begin="2:36.880" end="2:37.160">て</span> <span begin="2:37.160" end="2:37.390">繋</span><span begin="2:37.390" end="2:37.510">げ</span><span begin="2:37.510" end="2:37.780">て</span> <span begin="2:37.780" end="2:37.930">い</span><span begin="2:37.930" end="2:38.020">つ</span><span begin="2:38.020" end="2:38.120">の</span><span begin="2:38.120" end="2:38.460">日</span><span begin="2:38.460" end="2:38.630">に</span><span begin="2:38.630" end="2:38.890">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">传达心意 彼此连接 总有一天</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">傳達心意 彼此連接 總有一天</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Conveying it connecting it someday</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">전하고 이어서 언젠가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Transmets-les relie-les pour qu&apos;un jour</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Transmítelo conéctalo para que algún día</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gib es weiter verbinde es damit eines Tages</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Transmitindo conectando para que algum dia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Передавая связывая чтобы когда-нибудь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Trasmettilo connettilo e un giorno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsutaete tsunagete itsu no hi ni ka</span></p><p begin="2:39.070" end="2:41.300" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:39.070" end="2:39.460">涙</span><span begin="2:39.460" end="2:39.720">も</span><span begin="2:39.720" end="2:39.850">笑</span><span begin="2:39.850" end="2:40.070">顔</span><span begin="2:40.070" end="2:40.360">に</span><span begin="2:40.360" end="2:40.670">変</span><span begin="2:40.670" end="2:41.020">え</span><span begin="2:41.020" end="2:41.300">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">将泪水也化作笑容</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">將淚水也化作笑容</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Turning even tears into smiles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">눈물도 웃음으로 바꾸며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même les larmes se changent en sourires</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las lágrimas también se transformen en sonrisas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sich auch Tränen in ein Lächeln verwandeln</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Transforme até as lágrimas em sorrisos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Превратить даже слёзы в улыбки</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Trasforma anche le lacrime in sorrisi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Namida mo egao ni kaete</span></p><p begin="2:41.300" end="2:49.080" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:41.300" end="2:41.820">夢</span><span begin="2:41.820" end="2:42.150">を</span><span begin="2:42.150" end="2:42.420">見</span><span begin="2:42.420" end="2:43.230">続</span><span begin="2:43.230" end="2:43.580">け</span><span begin="2:43.580" end="2:43.860">る</span><span begin="2:43.860" end="2:44.840">こ</span><span begin="2:44.840" end="2:45.160">と</span><span begin="2:45.160" end="2:45.540">が</span><span begin="2:45.780" end="2:46.120">大</span><span begin="2:46.120" end="2:46.260">事</span><span begin="2:46.260" end="2:46.620">な</span><span begin="2:46.620" end="2:46.780">ん</span><span begin="2:46.780" end="2:49.080">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">坚持做梦才是最重要的啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">堅持做夢才是最重要的啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Continuing to dream is what is important</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">계속 꿈을 꾸는 것이 중요해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il est important de continuer à rêver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Lo importante es seguir soñando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und es ist wichtig weiterzuträumen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O importante é continuar sonhando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Важно продолжать мечтать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È importante continuare a sognare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yume o mitsuzukeru koto ga daiji nan da</span></p><p begin="2:59.480" end="3:04.040" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:59.480" end="2:59.650">ヒ</span><span begin="2:59.650" end="2:59.810">ト</span><span begin="2:59.810" end="3:00.020">と</span><span begin="3:00.020" end="3:00.470">人</span><span begin="3:00.470" end="3:00.790">形</span><span begin="3:00.790" end="3:01.080">の</span><span begin="3:01.080" end="3:01.760">違</span><span begin="3:01.760" end="3:02.010">い</span><span begin="3:02.010" end="3:02.230">は</span><span begin="3:02.230" end="3:02.390">ど</span><span begin="3:02.390" end="3:02.650">こ</span><span begin="3:02.650" end="3:02.810">に</span><span begin="3:02.810" end="3:03.020">あ</span><span begin="3:03.020" end="3:04.010">る</span><span begin="3:04.010" end="3:04.040">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">人类与人偶的区别究竟在哪里？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">人類與人偶的區別究竟在哪裡？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Where is the difference between humans and dolls?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">인간과 인형의 차이는 어디에 있을까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Où se trouve la différence entre les humains et les poupées ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Dónde está la diferencia entre un humano y una muñeca?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Worin liegt der Unterschied zwischen Mensch und Puppe?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Onde está a diferença entre humanos e bonecas?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В чём же разница между человеком и куклой?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dov&apos;è la differenza tra un umano e una bambola</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hito to ningyou no chigai wa doko ni aru?</span></p><p begin="3:03.650" end="3:09.140" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:03.650" end="3:03.890">も</span><span begin="3:03.890" end="3:04.130">し</span><span begin="3:04.130" end="3:04.280">か</span><span begin="3:04.280" end="3:04.520">し</span><span begin="3:04.620" end="3:04.950">た</span><span begin="3:04.950" end="3:05.250">ら</span><span begin="3:05.250" end="3:05.870">時</span><span begin="3:05.870" end="3:06.070">を</span><span begin="3:06.070" end="3:06.430">凍</span><span begin="3:06.430" end="3:06.680">ら</span><span begin="3:06.680" end="3:06.880">せ</span><span begin="3:06.880" end="3:07.530">て</span><span begin="3:07.530" end="3:07.830">る</span><span begin="3:07.830" end="3:07.980">だ</span><span begin="3:07.980" end="3:09.110">け</span><span begin="3:09.110" end="3:09.140">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">难道只是冻结了时间而已吗？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">難道只是凍結了時間而已嗎？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Maybe just freezing time?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어쩌면 시간을 얼려둔 것뿐일까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Peut-être qu&apos;elles ne font que figer le temps ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Acaso solo estamos congelando el tiempo?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Vielleicht ist nur die Zeit eingefroren?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Será que apenas estão congelando o tempo?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Может быть мы просто замораживаем время?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Forse stanno solo congelando il tempo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Moshikashitara toki o kooraseteru dake?</span></p><p begin="3:08.710" end="3:12.070" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:08.710" end="3:09.210">３</span><span begin="3:09.210" end="3:09.420">次</span><span begin="3:09.420" end="3:09.750">元</span> <span begin="3:09.750" end="3:09.870">４</span><span begin="3:09.870" end="3:09.960">次</span><span begin="3:09.960" end="3:10.380">元</span> <span begin="3:10.380" end="3:10.500">ど</span><span begin="3:10.500" end="3:10.600">こ</span><span begin="3:10.600" end="3:10.720">ま</span><span begin="3:10.720" end="3:10.980">で</span><span begin="3:10.980" end="3:11.210">進</span><span begin="3:11.210" end="3:11.350">化</span><span begin="3:11.350" end="3:11.630">を</span><span begin="3:11.630" end="3:11.830">経</span><span begin="3:11.830" end="3:12.070">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">历经三维 四维 无论进化到何种地步</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">歷經三維 四維 無論進化到何種地步</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">3rd dimension 4th dimension no matter how much evolution we go through</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">3차원 4차원 어디까지 진화를 거쳐서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Trois dimensions quatre dimensions peu importe jusqu&apos;où nous évoluons</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tercera dimensión cuarta dimensión hasta dónde evolucionaremos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dritte Dimension vierte Dimension egal wie weit wir evolvieren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">3ª dimensão 4ª dimensão até onde passaremos pela evolução</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Третье измерение четвёртое измерение пройдя эволюцию до каких пределов</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Terza dimensione quarta dimensione non importa quanta evoluzione attraversiamo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sanjigen yojigen doko made shinka o hete</span></p><p begin="3:12.250" end="3:17.090" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:12.250" end="3:12.400">ど</span><span begin="3:12.400" end="3:12.490">ん</span><span begin="3:12.490" end="3:12.620">な</span><span begin="3:12.620" end="3:12.800">に</span> <span begin="3:12.910" end="3:13.010">ど</span><span begin="3:13.010" end="3:13.130">ん</span><span begin="3:13.130" end="3:13.250">な</span><span begin="3:13.250" end="3:13.400">に</span> <span begin="3:13.510" end="3:13.730">神</span><span begin="3:13.730" end="3:14.190">様</span><span begin="3:14.190" end="3:14.490">へ</span><span begin="3:14.490" end="3:15.030">近</span><span begin="3:15.030" end="3:15.360">づ</span><span begin="3:15.360" end="3:15.670">い</span><span begin="3:15.670" end="3:16.000">た</span><span begin="3:16.000" end="3:16.120">と</span><span begin="3:16.120" end="3:16.450">し</span><span begin="3:16.450" end="3:16.700">た</span><span begin="3:16.700" end="3:16.960">っ</span><span begin="3:16.960" end="3:17.090">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论 无论 多么接近神明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論 無論 多麼接近神明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">No matter how much no matter how much we approach God</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아무리 아무리 신에게 가까워졌다 한들</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Peu importe peu importe à quel point nous nous approchons de Dieu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por mucho que por mucho que nos acerquemos a Dios</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Egal wie sehr egal wie sehr wir uns Gott nähern</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por mais por mais que nos aproximemos de Deus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Как бы сильно как бы сильно мы ни приблизились к богу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per quanto per quanto possiamo esserci avvicinati a Dio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Donna ni donna ni kamisama e chikazuita to shitatte</span></p><p begin="3:17.120" end="3:19.290" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:17.120" end="3:17.600">何</span><span begin="3:17.600" end="3:17.910">が</span><span begin="3:17.910" end="3:18.210">あ</span><span begin="3:18.210" end="3:18.520">る</span><span begin="3:18.520" end="3:18.690">と</span><span begin="3:18.690" end="3:18.910">云</span><span begin="3:18.910" end="3:19.260">う</span><span begin="3:19.260" end="3:19.290">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">又有什么意义呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">又有什麼意義呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">What is there to say?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">무엇이 있다는 걸까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Qu&apos;y a-t-il au bout du compte ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Qué es lo que dicen que habrá?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Was bedeutet das schon?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O que há lá afinal?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Что же там будет?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Cosa si suppone che ci sia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nani ga aru to iu?</span></p><p begin="3:19.580" end="3:22.200" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:19.580" end="3:20.100">今日</span><span begin="3:20.100" end="3:20.450">こ</span><span begin="3:20.450" end="3:20.750">の</span><span begin="3:20.750" end="3:21.240">愛</span><span begin="3:21.240" end="3:21.520">を</span><span begin="3:21.520" end="3:22.000">歌</span><span begin="3:22.000" end="3:22.200">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">此刻歌颂这份爱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">此刻歌頌這份愛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Singing this love today</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">오늘 이 사랑을 노래하며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Aujourd&apos;hui je chante cet amour</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hoy cantaré este amor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Heute singe ich diese Liebe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Hoje canto este amor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сегодня я пою эту любовь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Oggi canto questo amore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kyou kono ai o utai</span></p><p begin="3:22.200" end="3:32.090" itunes:key="L44" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:22.200" end="3:22.490">終</span><span begin="3:22.490" end="3:22.850">わ</span><span begin="3:22.850" end="3:22.960">っ</span><span begin="3:22.960" end="3:23.290">た</span><span begin="3:23.290" end="3:23.770">残</span><span begin="3:23.770" end="3:24.430">響</span><span begin="3:24.430" end="3:24.730">に</span><span begin="3:24.730" end="3:26.010">答</span><span begin="3:26.010" end="3:26.310">え</span><span begin="3:26.630" end="3:26.800">を</span><span begin="3:26.800" end="3:27.110">託</span><span begin="3:27.110" end="3:27.440">し</span><span begin="3:27.440" end="3:27.660">た</span><span begin="3:27.660" end="3:32.090">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">想要将答案托付给终结后的残响</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">想要將答案託付給終結後的殘響</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to entrust the answer to the finished reverberation</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">끝이 난 잔향에 해답을 맡기고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux confier la réponse à la réverbération achevée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero confiar la respuesta a la reverberación que ha terminado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und möchte die Antwort dem verhallenden Echo anvertrauen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero confiar a resposta à reverberação que terminou</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу доверить ответ отзвучавшему эху</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio affidare la risposta all&apos;eco che si è spenta</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Owatta zankyou ni kotae o takushitai</span></p><p begin="3:51.850" end="3:58.290" itunes:key="L45" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:51.850" end="3:52.160">ボ</span><span begin="3:52.160" end="3:52.500">ク</span><span begin="3:52.500" end="3:52.710">は</span><span begin="3:52.820" end="3:53.120">ボ</span><span begin="3:53.120" end="3:53.280">ク</span><span begin="3:53.280" end="3:53.470">の</span><span begin="3:53.470" end="3:53.940">物</span><span begin="3:53.940" end="3:54.580">語</span><span begin="3:54.580" end="3:54.930">を</span><span begin="3:55.200" end="3:55.560">運</span><span begin="3:55.560" end="3:55.830">命</span><span begin="3:55.830" end="3:55.950">の</span><span begin="3:55.950" end="3:56.190">せ</span><span begin="3:56.190" end="3:56.370">い</span><span begin="3:56.500" end="3:56.820">に</span><span begin="3:56.820" end="3:56.940">は</span><span begin="3:56.940" end="3:57.290">し</span><span begin="3:57.290" end="3:57.590">た</span><span begin="3:57.590" end="3:57.800">く</span><span begin="3:57.910" end="3:58.210">な</span><span begin="3:58.210" end="3:58.290">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我不愿将属于我的故事归咎于命运</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我不願將屬於我的故事歸咎於命運</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I don&apos;t want to blame my story on destiny</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나는 나의 이야기를 운명 탓으로 돌리고 싶지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne veux pas rejeter la faute de mon histoire sur le destin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No quiero culpar al destino por mi propia historia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich möchte meine Geschichte nicht dem Schicksal anlasten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu não quero culpar o destino pela minha história</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я не хочу винить судьбу в своей истории</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non voglio dare la colpa al destino per la mia storia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku wa boku no monogatari o unmei no sei ni wa shitakunai</span></p><p begin="3:58.540" end="4:02.740" itunes:key="L46" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:58.540" end="3:59.060">一</span><span begin="3:59.060" end="3:59.490">歩</span><span begin="3:59.810" end="4:00.180">一</span><span begin="4:00.300" end="4:00.570">歩</span><span begin="4:00.570" end="4:00.740">づ</span><span begin="4:00.740" end="4:00.920">つ</span><span begin="4:00.920" end="4:01.260">を</span><span begin="4:01.260" end="4:01.390">い</span><span begin="4:01.390" end="4:01.570">き</span><span begin="4:01.570" end="4:02.170">て</span><span begin="4:02.170" end="4:02.740">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一步一步切实地活下去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">一步一步切實地活下去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Living step by step</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">한 걸음 한 걸음씩 살아갈 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je vis en avançant pas à pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Voy viviendo paso a paso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gehe Schritt für Schritt durchs Leben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vou vivendo um passo de cada vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я буду жить шаг за шагом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Continuo a vivere passo dopo passo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ippo ippo zutsu o ikiteku</span></p><p begin="4:03.020" end="4:08.330" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:03.020" end="4:03.350">キ</span><span begin="4:03.350" end="4:03.510">ミ</span><span begin="4:03.510" end="4:03.680">の</span><span begin="4:03.680" end="4:04.160">物</span><span begin="4:04.160" end="4:04.820">語</span><span begin="4:04.820" end="4:05.130">は</span><span begin="4:05.420" end="4:05.630">ど</span><span begin="4:05.630" end="4:05.750">ん</span><span begin="4:05.750" end="4:05.900">な</span><span begin="4:05.900" end="4:06.590">輝</span><span begin="4:06.710" end="4:07.030">な</span><span begin="4:07.030" end="4:07.190">の</span><span begin="4:07.190" end="4:07.440">で</span><span begin="4:07.440" end="4:07.820">しょ</span><span begin="4:07.820" end="4:08.140">う</span><span begin="4:08.140" end="4:08.300">か</span><span begin="4:08.300" end="4:08.330">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你的故事又有着怎样的光辉呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你的故事又有著怎樣的光輝呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">What kind of radiance is your story?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너의 이야기는 어떤 빛을 내고 있을까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">De quel éclat brille ton histoire je me le demande ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Qué clase de brillo tiene tu historia?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In welchem Glanz erstrahlt wohl deine Geschichte?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que tipo de brilho tem a sua história?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Каким же сиянием наполнена твоя история?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Che tipo di splendore ha la tua storia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi no monogatari wa donna kagayaki na no deshou ka?</span></p><p begin="4:08.470" end="4:10.810" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:08.470" end="4:08.800">明日</span><span begin="4:08.800" end="4:09.060">の</span><span begin="4:09.060" end="4:09.230">キ</span><span begin="4:09.230" end="4:09.330">ミ</span><span begin="4:09.330" end="4:09.420">へ</span><span begin="4:09.420" end="4:09.700">と</span><span begin="4:09.700" end="4:09.970">伝</span><span begin="4:09.970" end="4:10.070">え</span><span begin="4:10.070" end="4:10.390">た</span><span begin="4:10.390" end="4:10.590">い</span><span begin="4:10.590" end="4:10.810">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">想要传达给明天的你啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">想要傳達給明天的你啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to convey it to you of tomorrow</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내일의 너에게 전하고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux le transmettre au toi de demain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero transmitírselo a tu yo del mañana</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich möchte es dem Du von morgen übermitteln</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero transmitir isso para o você de amanhã</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу передать это тебе в завтрашний день</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio trasmetterlo a te di domani</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ashita no kimi e to tsutaetai yo</span></p><p begin="4:10.980" end="4:13.180" itunes:key="L49" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:10.980" end="4:11.140">ジ</span><span begin="4:11.140" end="4:11.250">ブ</span><span begin="4:11.250" end="4:11.330">ン</span><span begin="4:11.330" end="4:11.630">の</span><span begin="4:11.630" end="4:11.880">色</span><span begin="4:11.880" end="4:11.970">し</span><span begin="4:11.970" end="4:12.290">た</span><span begin="4:12.290" end="4:12.920">歌</span><span begin="4:12.920" end="4:13.180">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那有着自我色彩的歌谣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那有著自我色彩的歌謠</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A song in my own color</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 고유의 색을 띤 노래가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Que cette chanson teintée de ma propre couleur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que una canción con mi propio color</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass ein Lied in meiner eigenen Farbe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A canção com a minha própria cor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чтобы песня окрашенная в мой цвет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Che la canzone dipinta del mio colore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jibun no iro shita uta ga</span></p><p begin="4:13.240" end="4:17.470" itunes:key="L50" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:13.240" end="4:13.570">こ</span><span begin="4:13.570" end="4:13.700">の</span><span begin="4:13.700" end="4:14.370">星</span><span begin="4:14.370" end="4:14.700">の</span><span begin="4:14.800" end="4:15.790">歴史</span><span begin="4:15.790" end="4:16.720">に</span><span begin="4:16.720" end="4:17.070">変</span><span begin="4:17.070" end="4:17.400">わ</span><span begin="4:17.400" end="4:17.470">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">化作这颗星球的历史</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">化作這顆星球的歷史</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Turns into the history of this planet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 별의 역사로 바뀌어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Se transforme en l&apos;histoire de cette planète</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se convierta en la historia de este planeta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zur Geschichte dieses Planeten wird</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se transforma na história deste planeta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Превратилась в историю этой планеты</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Si trasformi nella storia di questo pianeta</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono hoshi no kioku ni kawari</span></p><p begin="4:17.680" end="4:21.280" itunes:key="L51" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:17.680" end="4:18.070">風</span><span begin="4:18.070" end="4:18.210">に</span><span begin="4:18.210" end="4:18.730">還</span><span begin="4:18.730" end="4:21.280">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">回归风中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">回歸風中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Returning to the wind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">바람으로 돌아간다고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et retourne au vent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y regrese al viento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bevor es zum Wind zurückkehrt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E retorna ao vento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И вернулась к ветру</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E torni al vento</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kaze ni kaeru</span></p></div></body></tt>